title: VA: New Oldies - On My Way (Dutch Treat ^A168 HQ VBR MP3)
description:
Hi, between Oldies and Indie (alternative becomes mainstream) is a big gap. And there is where my mind then goes to. To give some random attention to these (transition) songs (New Oldies) in between the two periods.

As a collector I have all kinds of queues, waiting to be emptied. All tracks claiming to be played (sometime). So I jumped in (Donald) and let basically let the music do its thing. It looks like becoming a series of 3 New Oldies. This one is the first.

Warning: some songs come very close (to the heart).... Enjoy,
